name: NoTimeOverThere
description:
How long will you be able to save time? How long can you survive against someone stealing your time? 

NoTimeOverThere is my first and work in progress, published game. It's about survive against TimeEater, stealing their life time. 

Hit or Jump on enemies to steal their time but watch out dont get touched by them or they'll suck all the time you have.

Hope you can enjoy.
